 News Map is built upon cartogram.js (a JavaScript implementation of an algoritm to construct continuous area cartograms Â©1985), d3.js and colorbrewer. This visualization combines TopoJSON-encoded boundaries of the Chinese provinces with GDP data from National Bureau Statistics of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China to size each province proportionally. Designed and built by Chengjun Wang and Zhicong Chen at Computational Communication Collaboratory, School of Journalism and Communication, Nanjing University.
